\c 43
\s Abantu baya eGibhithe
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi lapho uJeremiya eseqedile ukukhuluma kubo bonke abantu wonke amazwi eN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wabo, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wabo eyayimthume ngawo kibo, \add ngitsho\add* wonke lamazwi;
\v 2 wasekhuluma uAzariya indodana kaHoshaya,\x + 42.1.\x* loJohanani indodana kaKareya,\x + 40.8.\x* labo bonke abantu abazikhukhumezayo,\x + Hlab. 86.14; 119.51. Isa. 13.11. Mal. 3.15; 4.1.\x* besithi kuJeremiya: Uqamba amanga. IN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu kayikuthumanga ukuze uthi: Lingayi eGibhithe ukuze lihlale njengabezizwe khona;\x + 42.19.\x*
\v 3 kodwa uBharukhi indodana kaNeriya\x + 32.12; 43 .6.\x* uyakukhuthaza emelene lathi,\x + 38.22.\x* ukuze asinikele esandleni samaKhaladiya,\x + 37.13.\x* ukuze asibulale, asithumbele eBhabhiloni.
\v 4 Ngakho uJohanani indodana kaKareya,\x + 40.8.\x* lazo zonke induna zamabutho,\x + 4 .5; 40.13.\x* labo bonke abantu, kabalilalelanga ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*, ukuze bahlale elizweni lakoJuda.
\v 5 Kodwa uJohanani indodana kaKareya\x + 40.8.\x* lazo zonke induna zamabutho\x + 40.13; 43.5.\x* bathatha yonke insali yakoJuda eyayibuyele ivela kuzo zonke izizwe lapho ababexotshelwe khona, ukuhlala elizweni lakoJuda;\x + 40.11,12.\x*
\v 6 amadoda,\x + 44.20.\x* labafazi,\x + 44.20.\x* labantwana, lamadodakazi enkosi,\x + 41.10.\x* laye wonke umuntu uNebuzaradani induna yabalindi ayebatshiye kuGedaliya indodana kaAhikhamu\x + 39.10; 40.7.\x* indodana kaShafani, loJeremiya umprofethi, loBharukhi indodana kaNeriya.\x + 32.12; 43.6.\x*
\v 7 Basebengena elizweni leGibhithe, ngoba kabalilalelanga ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*; basebefika eThahaphanesi.\x + 2.16.\x*
\p
\v 8 Laselifika ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* kuJeremiya eThahaphanesi\x + 2.16.\x* lisithi:
\v 9 Thatha esandleni sakho amatshe amakhulu, uwafihle ebumbeni ewondweni,\x + 2 Sam. 12.31.\x* esekungeneni kwendlu kaFaro eThahaphanesi,\x + 2.16.\x* emehlweni amadoda angamaJuda,
\v 10 uthi kiwo: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: Khangelani, ngizathuma ngilande uNebhukadirezari inkosi yeBhabhiloni inceku yami,\x + 25.9.\x* ngifake isihlalo sakhe sobukhosi phezu kwalamatshe engiwafihlileyo,\x + 1.15.\x* endlale ithente lakhe lesikhosini phezu kwawo.
\v 11 Eze atshaye ilizwe leGibhithe;\x + 44.13; 46.13.\x* labo abokufa ekufeni, lalabo abokuthunjwa ekuthunjweni, lalabo abenkemba enkembeni.\x + 15.2.\x*
\v 12 Ngiphembe umlilo\x + 17.27.\x* ezindlini zabonkulunkulu beGibhithe,\x + 43.13; 46.25. Hez. 30.13. Isa. 19.1. Eks. 12.12.\x* abatshise, abathumbe,\x + 48.7.\x* azithandele ngelizwe leGibhithe njengomelusi ezithandela ngesigqoko sakhe,\x + Hlab. 104.2. Isa. 49.18; 61.10.\x* aphume khona ngokuthula.
\v 13 Njalo uzakwephula insika zeBetshemeshi eziyizithombe\x + 50.2. Eks. 23.24.\x* eziselizweni leGibhithe,\x + Josh. 15.10; 19.22,38.\x* atshise ngomlilo izindlu zabonkulunkulu beGibhithe.\x + 43.13; 46.25. Hez. 30.13. Isa. 19.1. Eks. 12.12.\x*